## TV13 Design
Created AlphaTournamentV13Policy:
- Tracks consecutive idle steps (no alignment target available)
- After 150 idle steps: enters aggressive full-map exploration mode
- Uses 32 waypoints covering entire map (inner/mid/outer rings + corners)
- Each agent starts at different waypoint for spread coverage
- Still scrambles briefly (50/400 steps) to maintain pressure
- Immediately returns to alignment when new frontier junction discovered
- Based on TV9 (inherits 2-agent timing fix)

